Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_collec..._compatibility(25.10)    timing_collec..._compatibility(25.10)

Name
       timing_collection_variable_assignment_compatibility

Syntax
       timing_collection_variable_assignment_compatibility

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Disables printing the names of the output of get_* commands.

       When  set to false, the software prints the get_* command output on the
       shell. This global variable should be used for debugging purposes only.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

